  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h1>Adds</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Add support to port forward in the VPN cryptography</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Changes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Prevent environment names to include dot characters</li>\n<li>Remove GMX email provider from the blacklist of email providers</li>\n<li>Improve account creation UX for invited users who don't have an account yet</li>\n<li>Improve accessibility of truncated titles</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Fixes</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix periodic 401 errors when calling API</li>\n<li>Fix \"View Build Logs\" and \"View Deployment Logs\" links, pointing to the proper environment</li>\n<li>Fix wrong member's avatar in Builds page</li>\n<li>Fix sign up error when the user doesn't exist</li>\n<li>Fix deployment process when building from a branch other than master</li>\n</ul>"
      },
